        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Making Real Change
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
        <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-red-600/10 p-3">
                <.icon name="hero-heart-solid" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600" />
              </div>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-lg">Health & Nutrition</span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              Improve children's nutritional status and track BMI metrics for enrolled children.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-red-600/10 p-3">
                <.icon name="hero-academic-cap-solid" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600" />
              </div>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-lg">Education</span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              Increase school attendance and improve academic performance through proper nutrition.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-red-600/10 p-3">
                <.icon name="hero-users-solid" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600" />
              </div>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-lg">Community</span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              Build sustainable local food systems and create employment opportunities.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-red-600/10 p-3">
                <.icon name="hero-chart-bar-solid" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600" />
              </div>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-lg">Transparency</span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
              Provide real-time tracking and ensure accountability through data-driven reporting.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
